K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-1: a'arya shr'i ma h'a k'a la n'a ma dh'a ra n'i /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-3: 'phags pa dpal mgon po nag po zhes bya ba'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-7: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje'i gdan la bdud btul te mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas ring por ma lon pa zhig na byang chub kyi shing drung na bzhugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-8: bcom ldan 'das ga la ba de logs su lha'i sde dpon chen po'i tshogs kyi bdag po ma h'a k'a la 'dod khams kyi dbang phyug la dbang bsgyur ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-9: dpal mgon po nag po chen pos bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag 'tshal nas phyogs gcig tu 'dug ste 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:192b-11: bdag gi rig pa 'bul gyi bzhes su gsol /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-0: nyes par bltas pa rnams steng du gzhan 'phrul dbang byed la thug pa @193a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-2: 'og tu ni sems can dmyal ba la thug pa yan chad bcing ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-3: thad ka kho ra khor yug tu ni ri la thug pa tshun chad bcing ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-4: gzhan yang 'di bton pas gtsug lag khang dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-6: dug gsum nad kyi sman pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-10: srin po langka pu ri'i grong khyer gtan nas rlog pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-11: gnod sbyin gyi bu mo nam mkha'i glog ma sprin rdul du rlog pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-12: lha ma yin gyi bu mo nam mkha'i glog ma snying rdul du rlog pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-026:193a-13: dkon mchog gsum gyis bstan pa srung bar khas blangs shing dam bcas pa'o //
